{"tid":1792770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1224、1231將會係繼理大一役後街頭抗爭既成績表","createTime":"2019-12-22T01:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T04:24:08.000Z","uid":89966,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9baaffb765ec423d89e14b2ac03cd08bbbbbf2","tid":1792770,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:56:36.000Z","msg":"24號好似係第一次通宵遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕對係意義重大<br />\n平安夜黃藍兩陣營都會有人出街過節<br />\n仲要地點揀係油尖旺呢啲be water主場<br />\n要溝女陪家人老公老婆食飯就爽手食完返黎尖沙咀呀<br />\n今次無藉口話無車返屋企.和理非回合.有其他活動分散人數.宣傳不足啦<br />\n勇武手足想做乜交比自己決定<br />\n但和理非同一眾街坊一定要出黎撐場谷人數睇水<br />\n只要夠人就可以掩護手足 班狗更加唔敢落便衣出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全世界24號晚一定要出黎賀佢老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔要比勇武手足孤零零過平安夜呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdV747S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdV747S.jpg&h=ce628c2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bbd5d5d7fbba140d5a75df51612b0ef88574b59","tid":1792770,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:57:19.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"67734328f6d8beac21e633595ecb3e75be7211a7","tid":1792770,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T01:58:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f4c54da79b469a3694fcd4157e92a374141ea6c","tid":1792770,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"234bea338a5c0ede1a8233d5ff247517cc4874e6","tid":1792770,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"攬炒"},{"pid":"88a11ecfe193242159c8f76312d61f413d909ed2","tid":1792770,"uid":89966,"like":0